Package: translate-clipboard
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, yad, xclip, translate-shell
Maintainer: Leonardo Amaral <leonardo_amaral98@hotmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/devleonardoamaral/translate-clipboard
Description: Clipboard translator with yad GUI using translate-shell
 A lightweight Bash script that translates clipboard content and allows
 language selection with persistent preference. Supports editing the text
 before translation with a simple YAD GUI.
